  ('diplomatic-9e854390-moex-00139', 'diplomatic-9e854390', 'diplomatic-9e854390-moex-112-06c9aafe', 'sub-diplomatic-9e854390-01', NULL, 'essay', '「去風險」（De-risking）這一概念首先由歐盟執委會主席馮德萊恩
